text: The University of Texas at El Paso is a public university in El Paso, Texas, United States. It has about 20,000 students enrolled and it was founded in 1914. ==References== * ==Other websites== *The University of Texas at El Paso Category:University of Texas Category:Conference USA Category:El Paso, Texas Category:1914 establishments in the United States Category:1910s establishments in Texas
